105
00:06:00,800 --> 00:06:01,560
Try it!

106
00:06:01,640 --> 00:06:03,350
They are not poisonous.

107
00:06:17,240 --> 00:06:18,550
It's not bad.

108
00:06:19,080 --> 00:06:20,390
See? I told you.

109
00:06:20,840 --> 00:06:22,190
Are you serious?

110
00:06:30,840 --> 00:06:32,790
I'm good at baking.

111
00:06:34,080 --> 00:06:36,760
Did I work in a restaurant...

112
