117
00:06:57,760 --> 00:06:58,990
She is also Xiao Dong's dream girl.

118
00:06:59,640 --> 00:07:00,680
She is just a friend.

119
00:07:00,840 --> 00:07:02,590
Wait here, you two.

120
00:07:14,240 --> 00:07:15,430
I'm coming.

121
00:07:17,640 --> 00:07:18,430
Xiao Dong.

122
00:07:18,510 --> 00:07:19,240
Why are you here?

123
00:07:19,320 --> 00:07:20,590
-Hurry up!
-I need to talk to you.

124
00:07:21,720 --> 00:07:22,320
Come on in.

125
00:07:22,400 --> 00:07:23,270
Sure.

126
00:07:24,200 --> 00:07:26,040
Hello, pretty. Long time no see.

127
00:07:26,120 --> 00:07:27,800
I haven't seen you
since you became famous.

128
00:07:27,920 --> 00:07:29,480
It's because Xiao Dong
and you are always busy.

129
00:07:29,560 --> 00:07:29,960
Yes.

130
00:07:30,040 --> 00:07:31,540
We shall get back to work.

131
00:07:35,760 --> 00:07:37,990
What's wrong? Am I not welcome?

132
00:07:38,440 --> 00:07:39,000
Of course not.

133
00:07:39,080 --> 00:07:40,190
Come in.

134
00:07:41,920 --> 00:07:43,550
There is a girl in the house.

135
00:07:44,760 --> 00:07:47,060
That's Xiao Rui's cousin.

136
00:07:47,180 --> 00:07:48,810
Here, take a seat.

137
00:07:49,600 --> 00:07:52,470
[Do not squeeze]
You finally decide to move.

138
00:07:52,920 --> 00:07:54,370
