friend and his dream girl.

142
00:08:01,080 --> 00:08:02,400
Is Xu Xiao Dong in love with her?

143
00:08:02,480 --> 00:08:03,710
Not to that extent.

144
00:08:03,880 --> 00:08:05,880
However, she always
seeks help from Xu Xiao Dong

145
00:08:05,960 --> 00:08:07,510
and Xu Xiao Dong has
never turned her down.

146
00:08:07,590 --> 00:08:08,400
But it's normal.

147
00:08:08,480 --> 00:08:10,710
I don't think anyone
would say no to Qin Yue.

148
00:08:11,560 --> 00:08:12,830
It's just some random stuff.

149
00:08:14,800 --> 00:08:15,520
Xiao Dong.

150
00:08:15,600 --> 00:08:16,400
Today,

151
00:08:16,640 --> 00:08:18,320
I'm here to ask for a favour.

152
00:08:18,400 --> 00:08:19,670
What is it?

153
00:08:19,840 --> 00:08:21,070
Here it goes.

154
00:08:22,720 --> 00:08:24,190
Everyone,

155
00:08:24,320 --> 00:08:25,280
as we can see,

156
00:08:25,360 --> 00:08:27,400
both parties have come
to the middle of the stage.

157
00:08:27,480 --> 00:08:29,669
The goddess has made a move.

158
00:08:29,760 --> 00:08:32,120
Tomorrow, I have an important live-stream.

159
00:08:32,200 --> 00:08:34,480
I need you to monitor the background.

160
00:08:36,080 --> 00:08:37,040
Will my friend

161
00:08:37,120 --> 00:08:38,160
catch it?

162
00:08:38,240 --> 00:08:39,520
Sure, no problem.

163
00:08:39,600 --> 00:08:40,570
He got it.

164
00:08:40,880 --> 00:08:42,950
My friend got it.

165
00:08:43,030 --> 00:08:43,830
You agreed right away.

166
00:08:43,910 --> 00:08:44,640
Yes.

167
00:08:44,720 --> 00:08:46,140
No problem, it's just a small deal.

168
00:08:46,920 --> 00:08:48,070
That's great.

169
00:08:54,520 --> 00:08:55,740
What else do you need?

170
00:08:56,080 --> 00:08:57,000
The current situation

171
00:08:57,080 --> 00:08:58,440
