201
00:09:46,640 --> 00:09:47,440
It's an unbearable sight.

202
00:09:47,520 --> 00:09:48,520
Yes, it's a live-stream.

203
00:09:48,600 --> 00:09:49,400
All the best to you.

204
00:09:49,760 --> 00:09:50,440
